title: Minutemen Scans Event Pack - Secret Invasion
description:
Here it is friends. EVERYTHING. All Secret Invasion and Secret Invasion: The Infiltration issues in one convenient pack. Enjoy another organized, quality torrent from Sakrilege. Messy torrents with poorly named files = bad. Have some pride in your work people. DCP and the Minutemen do and so should you.


Event:
Secret Invasion Infiltration & Secret Invasion


Plot:
The shape-shifting alien race known as the Skrulls has secretly infiltrated every super-powered organization on Earth with one goal...full-scale invasion!



Event Pack Contains the following:

2nd and 3rd printing variants as well as many other variants and promo cards are included in this pack. Also the Infiltration issues (prelude to Secret Invasion) is included and in a separate folder.
